# Figma API Configuration
# Required for automatic token syncing
#
# To obtain a Figma Access Token:
# 1. Go to https://www.figma.com/developers/api#access-tokens
# 2. Click "Get personal access token"
# 3. Copy the token and paste it below
#
# To find your Figma File Key:
# 1. Open your Figma design system file
# 2. The file key is in the URL: https://www.figma.com/file/FILE_KEY/...
# 3. Copy the FILE_KEY and paste it below

FIGMA_FILE_KEY=your-figma-file-key-here
FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-figma-access-token-here
